For a double bed, everyone needs their own grate and mattress, but here be careful when buying to match the height of the mattress.
Otherwise, there will be nothing left but to mount the gratings to different heights, but you may not succeed with each bed frame.
Foam mattresses should have a height of at least 14 cm, types with a spring skeleton of at least 15, of which at least three centimeters count on the shaping and loosening layer.
"When touching your hands or sitting on the mattress, you definitely mustn't feel the springs," warns Helena Prokopová.
Each mattress requires a certain type of grid.
