And because we normally sweat 0.2 to 0.75 liters of sweat per night, it is clear that after five to seven years the mattress will start to resemble one large (and clogged) sieve.
Therefore, experts reject advertising slogans about the life of mattresses up to 25 years, or even lifetime warranty.
But everything has its buts.
That’s why the advice from the retailers: do not give up on mattresses with a width of 120 or 140 cm of hygiene and washable coating, but rather add a mattress protector that you can easily remove and wash.
Although mattress covers with slide fasteners all around the perimeter are commonly produced today, so we get two parts after opening (very important for washing and washing machine size!), yet the manipulation in larger types (and in one person) when shooting could resemble a duel of light weight in the ring with heavy.
Do you have a hardboard in your bed instead of a grate?
Never!
Maximum one-night stay on a bed.
However, keep the board (if it does not already have them) ventilated and use a mattress with a spring frame and a height of at least 15 cm with springs in bags (from it.Taschenfederkern) and a layer of loosening.
Polyurethane mattress does not belong on such a base.
Latex or sandwich mattresses (for example a combination of latex and coconut) will be suitable for non-positioning slats with 14 to 18 slats, but slats with a larger number of slats, 28 or more, where the slats are doubled in the lumbar area and their rigidity can be regulated.
There is no spring mattress on the positioning lamella grids because they do not respond to positioning.
In addition to setting the stiffness of the slats, you can also enjoy the so-called shoulder cradle.
It is a special attachment of the slats, which allows you to push or even tilt the slats so that the shoulder sleeps nicely.
For men who have "shoulders all over their backs", this is definitely an important thing.
It is even remembered by mattress manufacturers who have started to use the softening zone in the shoulder area.
Women also remember - they, in turn, give a softer surface in the hips.
For the most demanding customers aileron or plate gratings with so-called multitorsion suspension are designed.
The pressure is spread over more points and the tension is reduced.
However, be careful, as soon as you apply the wrong pillow (big and "enthusiastic") to the right mattress and grid, most of the "plus" will disappear.
The basic rule is simple: the pillow should support the head and only extend to the shoulders with the tips so that the shoulder muscles can relax.
A suitable size is recommended 50 x 60 cm, which they prefer, for example, in Scandinavia.
When lying on the side, the pillow should balance (along with the shoulder cradle of the grate or the softened zone in the mattress) the height of the shoulder.
Modern mattresses have something in common with the original straw-filled grasses.
