While men are “cooled” by birch plant extract to absorb heat and cool the body, women, on the contrary, “sink” the covers.
Red pepper extract increases blood circulation, making the weaker sex warmer.
Today's favorites?
Mattresses made of cold foam (has larger pores with broken cellular structure, is more breathable than ordinary polyurethane and offers better elasticity.
The combination of various stiffnesses of cold foam and "lazy" foam creates multi-zone mattresses that know exactly where the head, hips and heels should be.
For a quality mattress you will pay from seven thousand crowns and above.
Those that meet the health parameters, have a lower VAT rate, are treated as medical aids.
